Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================OP============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:46.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}茫茫人海行色匆匆　擦肩而过碰撞纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.05,0:01:52.97,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}感受彼此羽翼的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:59.16,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}用寂寞抱紧你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:05.61,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}无须其他任何表示
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.04,0:02:08.98,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}等候交融的瞬间　觉醒的永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.03,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}心急如焚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:18.56,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}时光荏苒转瞬即逝　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:28.03,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只能叹息　心愿遥不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:34.33,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}炽热的灵魂　传递真情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.53,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}不再有保留
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.69,0:02:43.88,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}你曾经的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:49.16,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}又在何方…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================ED============================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:11.85,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,1500)\an3}曾如此形影不离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:20.94,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(500,2500)}黄昏却已变色…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:37.28,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}平凡的温柔　让你远去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.53,0:22:45.01,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}被抛弃的心灵　四处彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:53.24,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}这份失落　如果就是生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.44,0:22:57.52,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}我愿在夜空下　从此闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:23:06.55,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\be1}曾形影不离　黄昏却已变色
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:17.77,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}{\be1}至少让我在月光下　静静入眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Avant============================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.E.70年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「血色情人节」的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.96,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导致地球与PLANT的紧张关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终升级为武力冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:20.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战前无人怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军将以数量优势取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现实出乎所有人的预料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战局陷入拉锯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看即将进入第11个月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救生艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:51.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我算是看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很喜欢捡破烂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.61,0:01:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.72,0:01:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 各位辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================Main============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:57.42,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1184,576)}{\fad(500,500)}{\bord3\shad1\be20\an3\fs60}敌军歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀 唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.40,0:03:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这不是扎夫特的船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,识别编号：285002
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克鲁泽队所属 阿斯兰·萨拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军总部通知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯提前35小时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,予明日18:00出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员1小时前集合登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复述后请回复
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯明日18:00出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员1小时前集合 登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰·萨拉 收到命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次追悼团代表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝·克莱茵小姐也乘坐这艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去向不明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为举行周年纪念典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.85,0:05:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往尤尼乌斯7号的追悼团视察船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银风号 昨晚失去联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们出手相救
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 拉克丝 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的朋友 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听不见 别说话多尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的搬运工作都完成了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莱茵…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT最高议会议长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像就叫西格尔·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 西格尔·克莱茵是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的人怎么会来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.92,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我此行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为尤尼乌斯7追悼典礼做事前准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的船遭遇地球军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.26,0:06:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方要求临检
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们便接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.54,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们的航行目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎让地球军的军官们非常不快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从很小的口角
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发展成很大的骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时 身边的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我送上救生艇逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你的船现在呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球军的军官们息怒就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅萨琉斯按时出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘员请从12号门迅速登舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝的事听说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…队长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非梅萨琉斯就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 真是个铁石心肠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然是去搜寻她的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 还不一定就是遇难
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.92,0:08:14.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是民用船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过没有公布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先行前往调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翁洛队的侦查Ginn也一去不归
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤尼乌斯7号被地球引力捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现漂流在碎石带中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很棘手的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡莫夫自阿尔狄弥斯之战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就丢失了长腿的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.64,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个PLANT都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝和你已定终身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时你所在的克鲁泽队
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能继续休假
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是国民的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 克鲁泽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.02,0:08:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我像英雄那样救她回来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱着她的遗骸痛哭着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.93,0:09:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去首先就不成体统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨拉委员长认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗元气哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你元气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起祈祷吧 哈罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:10:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有逝者的灵魂 都可以安息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Ginn 难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不去就不去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.54,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了给那个女人的饭菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽要芙蕾送去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.30,0:10:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾不肯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就吵起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 基拉不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可她是扎夫特的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人不只是头脑好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.21,0:11:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕一万就怕万一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.49,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.79,0:11:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我想她没凶到那种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人的能力 外表根本看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一力气很大怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.94,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁力气很大啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 元气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.64,0:11:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给的问题刚解决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.75,0:12:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来个粉红色头发的公主小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.61,0:12:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦心事一件接一件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长同志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然上船 只能带她去月球总部了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上不会靠港了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是去到月球总部的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她是平民…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.59,0:12:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是夹道欢迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是克莱茵家的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用价值自不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 我不希望她受到那种待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个平民少女 还那么不谙世事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要是这么说的话 那他们呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.65,0:12:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助驾船 参与战斗的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只是平民中的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴基露露少尉 话不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对基拉·大和和他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:13:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以形势所迫为由进行征召
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到那个少女却不希望她卷进战争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.18,0:13:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是想这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身为克莱茵的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅凭这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就不是一个普通的平民了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉惊扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.46,0:13:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗓子渴得厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.46,0:13:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 别笑我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实肚子也饿得咕咕叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是餐厅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能给一些吃的会感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间没锁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特的女人为什么能擅自到处走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是擅自
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在屋里大声问过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「可以出去吗」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且问了三次！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 我不是扎夫特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扎夫特是军队的名称
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:03.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全称是自由条约黄道联盟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是军人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看来也不是军队里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉忘记自我介绍 我叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.09,0:14:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么要和你握手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调整人少来厚颜无耻地套近乎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 来玩来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不承认 绝不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾是「蓝色宇宙」的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他们说得话又没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没生病的人去调整遗传基因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.32,0:15:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是违背自然规律的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错误的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实大家都这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.15,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又必须呆在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊啊 整天一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想在那里和大家边聊天边吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是地球军的军舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对调整人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说…不太喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在又是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉克丝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你对我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认没错吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.58,0:17:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是地球军第八舰队的密码脉冲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解读吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解析完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 第八舰队先遣队…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙哥马利…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大天使号 请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哈尔巴顿准将旗下的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是在找我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 位置距离还很远
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要会合了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 总算不用提心吊胆了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米丽跟说我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:17:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会跟芙蕾说的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:16.40,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}静静的夜里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:32.91,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}等你拾回忘却的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:45.76,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}那件事已过好久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:57.78,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}记忆也磨去了棱角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:08.20,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}在流星划落的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:21.21,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}祈祷你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:27.31,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}即便天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:35.86,utacn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1\an3}终会相见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我也是调整人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:18:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你对我好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是因为这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉·大和
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 基拉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她在唱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.62,0:19:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过归根到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是操纵基因得到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.32,0:19:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也得去填饱肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是容易忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基拉也是调整人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能轻松地开着去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是地球军舰艇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们在这种地方干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长腿如果想从阿尔狄弥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.91,0:20:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长途跋涉到月球总部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会如何做？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么首先是补给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是指望来迎接的舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的位置还未暴露是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾随他们 不要被发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然没有忘记拉克丝·克莱茵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为了区区一个少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视而不见是否合适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被后世的历史学家嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方位45.01A
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成航向修正
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎60%功率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可算有指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知多久才能会合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.85,0:21:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘船我待够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 跟先遣队一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾在船上的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经把名单发过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把动量几何偏移值改了下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你记得看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 最好是用不上这家伙了 今后
